Hungary Should Probe Simor’s Personal Finances, Szijjarto Says

-- B y   Z o l t a n   S i m o n
-- 
2011-10-18T07:30:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-18/hungary-should-probe-simor-s-personal-finances-szijjarto-says.html
 The Hungarian Parliament’s budget
committee should probe central bank President Andras Simor’s
personal finances,  Peter Szijjarto , Prime Minister  Viktor
Orban ’s spokesman, said at a hearing today.  Szijjarto wants Simor to present proof to the committee
that he has repatriated savings from Cyprus.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
